<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<body>
  <main class="solution-container">
    <article class="solution">
      <h1>Increase Retention for a Language Learning App</h1>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Solution Breakdown</h2>
        <p>
          This solution is to help users retain more of what they learn in the
          language learning app. It consists of an AI-powered feature that
          allows users to practice and remember words and phrases in a more
          effective way. The feature will be available as part of the app's
          premium subscription.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Approach</h2>
        <p>
          We will use AI to create personalized flashcards for each user. These
          flashcards will be generated based on the user's learning history and
          preferences. The AI will also optimize the timing and frequency of the
          flashcards to maximize retention.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Benefits</h2>
        <p>
          The personalized flashcards will make learning more efficient and
          enjoyable for users. They will be able to remember more of what they
          learn and progress faster in their language learning journey. This
          will increase user satisfaction and engagement with the app.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Potential Impact</h2>
        <p>
          By helping users retain more of what they learn, this solution can
          significantly improve the effectiveness of the language learning app.
          It can lead to higher user retention, longer subscription periods, and
          increased word-of-mouth referrals. Ultimately, it can contribute to
          the app's growth and success in the competitive language learning
          market.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section feedback">
